shop our cute sticker designs perfect for sticking onto laptops, water
bottles, planners and journals or any flat surface. Featuring adorable designs
that you won't find anywhere else, our range of high quality stickers are
designed to bring more happiness and humour to your daily life.

### A little about us

### A little about us

Toastedink is a British art brand built with the sole mission of spreading
more happiness across the globe. We are here to create a space for everyone to
step outside of reality and into a place of happiness through cute products,
cards, gifts and designs that you won't find anywhere else.  
  
We are here to promote positivity, empower you to live a better, happier life
and improve mental health in any way we can, and if we can do it through our
CUTE cards and stationery designs that will make you smile even that little
bit more, we will feel complete.
